Description: About Me: I’m an avid collector of music gear, and a semi-professional musician. I've been collecting and selling gear as a hobby for over a decade and have developed a keen eye for detail. As the former Showroom Manager of one of the top boutique guitar shops, I've had the opportunity to work with some of the most acclaimed builders in the world. Many of the guitars in my collection are brand new, acquired as an authorized dealer of a number of high-end brands.All the specs that you would want for top-notch playability but on a traditional J platform. The new Performer series Jazzmasters are exceptional - killer finish, tight neck pocket, vintage trem, jumbo frets, and great pups. Amazing playability with low, fast action, and excellent acoustic resonance. One of the LIGHTEST builds out there! ONLY 7.6lbs!
